      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BOBBYS ROOM NZ (4) lines up for the first time. By top sire Bettors Delight and hails from the McLean stable. Looked above average in winning the latest trial and should be ready to run a big race. CARAPAZ (10) has raced two times this campaign and has filled a minor placing on each occasion. Went back from a similar draw last start then worked home in good style to finish just 4.5 metres from the winner in second at Melton. Leading hope. SPORTY ROCKS (8) is at the track for the first time. By Sportswriter and hails from the Rebecca East stable. Trial winner who should enjoy a pretty soft run from this draw, with the sprint lane in play. FIVE CENT (1) has been tickling along okay from wider or second row barriers and should not have any excuses from the favourable draw.",
